OL,3,CConsumer confidence falls again amid
OL,4,C'despondent mood' ahead of October
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FConsumer confidence has fallen again
OL,8,Famid further worsening sentiment
OL,9,Faround the upcoming autumn Budget,
OL,10,Faccording to a long-running survey.
OL,12,FGfK's Consumer Confidence Index fell
OL,13,Fone point in October to minus 21, as
OL,14,Fpeople's predictions for the general
OL,15,Feconomy worsened over the coming year
OL,16,Fdespite a slight improvement in their
OL,17,Fforecasts for personal finances.
