OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FThe drop was significantly less than
OL,8,Fthe seven-point plunge in September.
OL,9,FExperts said that was also driven by
OL,10,FLabour's gloomy messaging around the
OL,11,Fspending statement in late October.
OL,13,FChancellor Rachel Reeves has
OL,14,Frepeatedly warned of "tough choices"
OL,15,Fto tackle what she has called a worse-
OL,16,Fthan-expected inheritance from the
OL,17,Fprevious Conservative government.
