OL,3,CConsumer confidence falls again amid
OL,4,C'despondent mood' ahead of October
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FNeil Bellamy, consumer insights
OL,8,Fdirector at GfK, said consumers are
OL,9,Fstill in a "despondent mood" despite a
OL,10,Frecent fall in the headline rate of
OL,11,Finflation.
OL,13,FHe added: "This month's Consumer
OL,14,FConfidence Barometer paints a picture
OL,15,Fof people holding their breath to see
OL,16,Fwhat's in store for them on October
OL,17,F30."
