OL,7,FInflation fell to a three-year low
OL,8,Fearlier in October, which some
OL,9,Feconomists say virtually guarantees
OL,10,Fthe Bank of England will cut interest
OL,11,Frates at its next policy meeting in
OL,12,FNovember.
OL,14,FCutting rates could encourage further
OL,15,Ffalls in mortgage rates, making things
OL,16,Feasier for would-be homebuyers.
