OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FThat did not improve perceptions of
OL,8,Fhow the wider economy will do in the
OL,9,Fcoming year. GfK's measure of
OL,10,Fexpectations for the general economic
OL,11,Fsituation over the next 12 months fell
OL,12,Fone point to minus 28.
OL,14,FThe forecast for personal finances
OL,15,Fover the next 12 months improved by
OL,16,Fone point at minus two, however, which
OL,17,Fis six points higher than this time
OL,18,Flast year.
