OL,4,C'despondent mood' ahead of October
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FThe consumer poll comes after a
OL,8,Fclosely-watched survey measuring
OL,9,Fbusiness confidence also showed
OL,10,Fworsening conditions ahead of the
OL,11,FBudget.
OL,13,FActivity across the UK's private
OL,14,Fsector slipped to an 11-month low in
OL,15,FOctober, according to the S&P Global
OL,16,Fflash UK composite purchasing
OL,17,Fmanagers' index.
