OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,F"Rising energy costs, winter fuel
OL,8,Fallowance cuts and the potential
OL,9,Finclusion of pension-related measures
OL,10,Fin the forthcoming Budget may be
OL,11,Ffactors that are reflected in this
OL,12,Ffinding," she said.
OL,14,F"The link between consumer confidence
OL,15,Fand spending is not as strong as
OL,16,Fhistorically, so retailers and their
OL,17,Fsuppliers will be hoping that they can
OL,18,Foutperform consumer confidence through
OL,19,FBlack Friday and Christmas."
